                <h1>Discover the Genius of Nikola Tesla: The Father of Modern Electricity</h1>
                <p>Nikola Tesla was a visionary inventor and electrical engineer known for developing alternating current (AC) electricity supply systems. His innovations laid the groundwork for modern electrical power systems, radio, and wireless technology. Tesla's dream of harnessing renewable energy continues to inspire generations of scientists and inventors.</p>
